[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":299},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190516\u002F3658238475\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190516\u002F3658238475\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190516\u002F3658238475\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190516\u002F3658238475\u002F":275,"related:\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190516\u002F3658238475\u002F":284},"\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fjs-weird-world-16-operator-precedence-associativity\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":258,"date":259,"description":260,"extension":261,"lang":262,"meta":263,"navigation":138,"path":264,"readingMinutes":265,"seo":266,"standalone":267,"stem":268,"tags":269,"tldr":272,"updated":272,"url":273,"__hash__":274},"content\u002FJavaScript 奇怪的部分\u002FJS奇怪的世界-No-16-運算子的優先性與相依性.md","[JS奇怪的世界]No.16 運算子的優先性與相依性","3658238475",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":252},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,29,32,35,40,43,46,104,115,126,129,235,238,241,248],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"運算子的優先性與相依性",[16,17,18],"p",{},"這兩個名詞在 JavaScript 是一個非常重要的東西，而且是非常重要的觀念，如果能瞭解其觀念，對於 debug 上也是有一定幫助的。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"運算子的優先性",[16,23,24],{},[25,26],"img",{"alt":27,"src":28},"圖片","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FzrPNBhMh.png",[16,30,31],{},"運算子的優先性的意思是表示哪一個運算子會被優先運算，因為一般來講一個運算子來講不一定會只有一個，而 JavaScript 會優先處理優先性較高的運算子依序到最低。",[12,33,34],{"id":34},"運算子的相依性",[16,36,37],{},[25,38],{"alt":27,"src":39},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fkd364yrh.png",[16,41,42],{},"運算子的相依性是什麼?相依性代表的是運算子被計算的順序，通常要馬是從左至右的相依性而這叫做左相依性，不然就是從右至左。",[16,44,45],{},"所以當一條運算中有兩個相同的優先性，那麼相依性就會很重要，相依性可以用來判斷要從右至左還是從左至右，課程提供了一個範例。",[47,48,53],"pre",{"className":49,"code":50,"language":51,"meta":52,"style":52},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","var a = 3 + 4 * 5;\nconsole.log(a);\n","js","",[54,55,56,91],"code",{"__ignoreMap":52},[57,58,61,65,69,72,76,79,82,85,88],"span",{"class":59,"line":60},"line",1,[57,62,64],{"class":63},"sWyjQ","var",[57,66,68],{"class":67},"sMAXC"," a ",[57,70,71],{"class":63},"=",[57,73,75],{"class":74},"sCcAr"," 3",[57,77,78],{"class":63}," +",[57,80,81],{"class":74}," 4",[57,83,84],{"class":63}," *",[57,86,87],{"class":74}," 5",[57,89,90],{"class":67},";\n",[57,92,94,97,101],{"class":59,"line":93},2,[57,95,96],{"class":67},"console.",[57,98,100],{"class":99},"sj_SG","log",[57,102,103],{"class":67},"(a);\n",[16,105,106,107,110,111,114],{},"答案會是多少?23，我們先思考一下數學規則，先乘除後加減，所以會 JavaScript 也是一樣的道理，所以 JavaScript 會先處理 ",[54,108,109],{},"4 * 5"," 處理完之後再 ",[54,112,113],{},"+ 3","。",[16,116,117,118,125],{},"那 JavaScript 的優先順序怎麼看? 課程中有附上 ",[119,120,124],"a",{"href":121,"rel":122},"https:\u002F\u002Fdeveloper.mozilla.org\u002Fen-US\u002Fdocs\u002FWeb\u002FJavaScript\u002FReference\u002FOperators\u002FOperator_Precedence",[123],"nofollow","MDN 的文件","連結可供我們去瞭解運算子的優先順序，而數字越大(Precedence)代表優先度越高。",[16,127,128],{},"在這邊課程就有提供一個不錯的範例",[47,130,132],{"className":49,"code":131,"language":51,"meta":52,"style":52},"\nvar a = 2;\nvar b = 3;\nvar c = 4;\n\na = b = c;\n\nconsole.log(a);\nconsole.log(b);\nconsole.log(c);\n",[54,133,134,140,153,167,181,186,201,206,215,225],{"__ignoreMap":52},[57,135,136],{"class":59,"line":60},[57,137,139],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":138},true,"\n",[57,141,142,144,146,148,151],{"class":59,"line":93},[57,143,64],{"class":63},[57,145,68],{"class":67},[57,147,71],{"class":63},[57,149,150],{"class":74}," 2",[57,152,90],{"class":67},[57,154,156,158,161,163,165],{"class":59,"line":155},3,[57,157,64],{"class":63},[57,159,160],{"class":67}," b ",[57,162,71],{"class":63},[57,164,75],{"class":74},[57,166,90],{"class":67},[57,168,170,172,175,177,179],{"class":59,"line":169},4,[57,171,64],{"class":63},[57,173,174],{"class":67}," c ",[57,176,71],{"class":63},[57,178,81],{"class":74},[57,180,90],{"class":67},[57,182,184],{"class":59,"line":183},5,[57,185,139],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":138},[57,187,189,192,194,196,198],{"class":59,"line":188},6,[57,190,191],{"class":67},"a ",[57,193,71],{"class":63},[57,195,160],{"class":67},[57,197,71],{"class":63},[57,199,200],{"class":67}," c;\n",[57,202,204],{"class":59,"line":203},7,[57,205,139],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":138},[57,207,209,211,213],{"class":59,"line":208},8,[57,210,96],{"class":67},[57,212,100],{"class":99},[57,214,103],{"class":67},[57,216,218,220,222],{"class":59,"line":217},9,[57,219,96],{"class":67},[57,221,100],{"class":99},[57,223,224],{"class":67},"(b);\n",[57,226,228,230,232],{"class":59,"line":227},10,[57,229,96],{"class":67},[57,231,100],{"class":99},[57,233,234],{"class":67},"(c);\n",[16,236,237],{},"答案會是 4，原因是在運算只優先度情況之下，它就會依照相依性來決定執行順序，而等號就是從右至左。",[12,239,240],{"id":240},"圖源",[16,242,243],{},[119,244,247],{"href":245,"rel":246},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.udemy.com\u002Fjavascriptjs\u002F",[123],"JavaScript 全攻略:克服 JS 奇怪的部分",[249,250,251],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":52,"searchDepth":93,"depth":93,"links":253},[254,255,256,257],{"id":14,"depth":93,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":93,"text":21},{"id":34,"depth":93,"text":34},{"id":240,"depth":93,"text":240},"克服JS奇怪的部分系列","2019-05-16 20:34:35","這兩個在 JavaScript 是一個非常重要的名詞，其實非常重要的觀念，如果能瞭解其觀念，對於 debug 上是有一定幫助的。","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fjavascript\u002Fjs-no-16","1",{"title":6,"description":260},false,"JavaScript 奇怪的部分\u002FJS奇怪